---
title: Cheat's Loaded Pork Jacket Potatoes with Sour Cream & Chives
description: Take a shortcut on the trusty jacket potato by giving it a spin in the microwave. Top it all off with American spiced pork, a good helping of Cheddar cheese and a dollop of sour cream!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d64b09b9271b9000d16e33c-d0621c57.jpg
